---

<section class="container-blog py-24 sm:py-32 text-center animate-fade-in-up">
  <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
    Digital Marketing
    <br />
    <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-primary to-rose-400">
      Made Simple & Free
    </span>
  </h1>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    Actionable insights on SEO, social media, content marketing, PPC, and analytics — written by Ketan Jawale. No jargon, no fluff.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
    <a href="/blog" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary text-black font-semibold hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all duration-150">Read Latest Posts</a>
    <a href="/about" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-border-default text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-150">About Ketan</a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
    <a href="/categories/seo" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider border border-tag-seo/30 text-tag-seo bg-tag-seo/5 hover:bg-tag-seo/10 transition-colors">SEO</a>
    <a href="/categories/social-media" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider border border-tag-social/30 text-tag-social bg-tag-social/5 hover:bg-tag-social/10 transition-colors">Social Media</a>
    <a href="/categories/content-marketing" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider border border-tag-content/30 text-tag-content bg-tag-content/5 hover:bg-tag-content/10 transition-colors">Content</a>
    <a href="/categories/ppc" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider border border-tag-ppc/30 text-tag-ppc bg-tag-ppc/5 hover:bg-tag-ppc/10 transition-colors">PPC</a>
    <a href="/categories/analytics" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider border border-tag-analytics/30 text-tag-analytics bg-tag-analytics/5 hover:bg-tag-analytics/10 transition-colors">Analytics</a>
  </div>
</section>
